OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain some of which will be heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes, but there should be a few drier
OL,8,Finterludes too, especially later.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FCloudy with spells of showery
OL,11,Frain, and murky conditions developing
OL,12,Fin the southwest. Rain will be locally
OL,13,Fheavy at times in the evening before
OL,14,Fbecoming briefly drier for a time.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA partly cloudy day with
OL,17,Fshowers or longer spells of rain,
OL,18,Foften rather heavy with a risk of
OL,19,Fthunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
